        <p className="text-gray-300 mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          To access your Google Drive files, this app requires a <strong>Google Cloud Client ID</strong>. 
          This is a security requirement by Google to allow this website to communicate with your Drive.
        </p>

        <ol className="list-decimal list-inside text-xs text-gray-400 mb-4 space-y-1">
            <li>Go to <a href="https://console.cloud.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" className="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Google Cloud Console</a>.</li>
            <li>Create a project and enable the <strong>Google Drive API</strong>.</li>
            <li>Go to Credentials → Create Credentials → <strong>OAuth Client ID</strong>.</li>
